pullRequest.title: Android- check style linter fixes
pullRequest.bodyText:
1.Method/Parameter must match pattern '^[a-z][a-z0-9][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$'. (Except for db class, db variable, api pojo classes).
2.'package' should be separated from previous statement.
3.Distance between variable 'X' declaration and its first usage is X, but allowed X.
4.Abbreviation in name 'X' must contain no more than 2 consecutive capital letters.
5.'if' and 'else' construct must use '{}'s.
6.Incorrect indentation label X expected level should be one of the following: X.
7.Extra separation in import group before X
